    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>买了新电脑后，需要重新安装Hexo，遇到了很多异常</p>
<h2 id="一些异常">一些异常</h2><p><strong>注意一定要装Xcode，我就是因为没有安装导致的各种异常</strong></p>
<p>其他参考: </p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues/913" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues/913</a></p>
<p><a href="http://wp.huangshiyang.com/hexo%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88" target="_blank" rel="external">http://wp.huangshiyang.com/hexo%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88</a></p>
<p><a href="http://xuanwo.org/2014/08/14/hexo-usual-problem/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://xuanwo.org/2014/08/14/hexo-usual-problem/</a></p>
<h2 id="简明步骤">简明步骤</h2><p><strong><em>环境：版本10.10.3</em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>安装</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>创建一个文件夹，eg.hexo</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>初始化</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>之后会出现：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[info] Copying data&#10;[info] You are almost done! Don&#39;t forget to run `npm install` before you start b&#10;logging with Hexo!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>执行上面命令</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>验证</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g&#10;hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>一切顺利的话会出现：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://0.0.0.0:4000/. Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>附上一个非常详细的教程：</p>
<p><a href="http://cnfeat.com/2014/05/10/2014-05-11-how-to-build-a-blog/" target="_blank" rel="external">如何搭建一个独立博客——简明Github Pages与Hexo教程</a></p>
]]></content>
    
